{
  "stem": "19969.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 73.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They have no nation, no country so nobody ever hardly mentions the gypsies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But when you look at the Nazi records, that was a group that was discriminated against terribly and executed promptly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They don't go to labor camps or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There weren't a great number of them, but nobody knows how many, but it was many thousands.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one religion that I found out in my-- all the books I read about Dachau were discriminated against the same way was Jehovah's Witnesses.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, that was a very, very small group in Germany, but they were considered in the same light as the gypsies.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And probably only a few of them, but they were promptly executed, along with the gypsies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Of course, we have Jehovah's Witnesses in this country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's a fairly large organization.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it was-- they had a small organization in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The other group, religion, that was discriminated against by the Germans were the Catholics.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Catholic priests were simply rounded up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they were part of the original group that was sent to Dachau starting in 1933.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when they invaded Poland and took over Poland, the Catholic priests, most of them went to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was another group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they did not-- it appears no record of actual extermination of the priests.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some executed, but because they were-- they got rebellious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- but even the Lutheran, which Germany is predominantly Lutheran, Pastor Niemoller was one of the leaders of the Lutheran Church in Germany, in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He finally spoke out against Hitler and he was put in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, he and some of the other important prisoners that were in Dachau were taken out of Dachau several weeks before we arrived.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were not there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
